Text: Hey buddy, Mr. (or Mrs. I suppose) Sportsaction666, do you think you could make a better version of this (my favorite) Renaldo & The Loaf album, like a FLAC (Free Lossless Audio Codec) or some other lossless codec. There are free, safe online programs with which you could accomplish this Exact Audio Copy for example. It is out of print so what the heck? Thanks... and may SATAN not bother you to much.
